    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twinkle Hunter is boss rush game with action's element. It is greatly inspired from Cuphead made by Studio MDHR, 2017.</h2><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266740/extras/Produce.GIF?t=1723019094\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various Bosses</h2><br>About 20 thieves with various design and movement threat you. As a hunter, you must arrest them interrupting you and finally retrieve your teddy bear from Plague, a member of thieves.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266740/extras/캡처2.PNG?t=1723019094\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging Combat, the key is DODGING</h2><br>Thieves will fight with all their might. Sometimes a strong boss may make you despair, but it makes the sense of victory bigger. When you fight with them, attack is important, but the key is dodging their attack.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266740/extras/8452f2f6867e8ea3fd837558f2b4a589.avif?t=1723019094\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change your equipment for the battle!</h2><br>From Active Skills for a mighty attack to Charms for new actions! Use around 20 equipments to make your gameplay various and attack bosses' weakness.",
